    "description": "Nippon Chuzo K. K. engages in supplying large, special, and steel castings for construction in Japan. The company also provides steel materials, cast iron, new casting technologies and formed and fabricated materials, and particularly for casting maIt is also involved in Engineering services in relation to bearings and expansion joints; and Construction materials for NC base plates, and buildings and structures products. In addition, it provides space and defense, semiconductor and LCD production, construction machinery, energy systems, waste incineration, industrial presses, iron production, casting systems, mighty bar, hydraulic components. Further, the company provides pivot bearing, pivot roller bearing, pin bearing, pin roller bearing, pot bearing, spherical bearing, line bearing, horizontal bearing, rubber bearings, function-separated bearing, super high-damping rubber bearing, super high-damping rubber bearings for cold climates, horizontal force dispersing rubber bearing, disc rubber bearing, expansion joints, swivel joint, and maurer joint. Additionally, it offers damper units, such as Joining brackets, square to round joints, NC nodes, and joining pins; and construction hardware and landscaping products, including Joining brackets, square to round joints, NC nodes, joining pins, construction materials section, and NC base plate. The company was founded in 1920 and is headquartered in Kawasaki, Japan."
